* CDNs
* Reverse proxy

---

## 2Ô∏è‚É£ Scaling Concepts

* Vertical vs Horizontal scaling
* Stateless vs Stateful services
* Load balancing

  * Layer 4 vs Layer 7
  * Round robin
  * Least connections
* Auto-scaling groups

---

## 3Ô∏è‚É£ Databases

### SQL (ACID)

* MySQL
* PostgreSQL
* Master-slave replication
* Sharding
* Indexing strategies

### NoSQL (BASE)

* Key-value (Redis)
* Document (MongoDB)
* Wide-column (Cassandra/HBase)
* Graph (Neo4j)

### Theory

* CAP Theorem
* PACELC
* Strong vs Eventual consistency
* Read replicas
* Partition tolerance

---

## 4Ô∏è‚É£ Caching

* Cache-aside
* Write-through
* Write-back
* Write-around
* LRU / LFU / TTL
* Multi-layer caching (CDN + App + DB)

---

## 5Ô∏è‚É£ Messaging & Async Processing

* Queue vs Stream
* Pub/Sub
* Kafka vs RabbitMQ
* At-least-once vs Exactly-once
* Idempotency
* SAGA pattern

---

## 6Ô∏è‚É£ Storage

* Blob storage (S3-like)
* Block storage
* File storage
* Object storage
* Chunking
* Deduplication

---

## 7Ô∏è‚É£ Reliability & Resilience

* Circuit breaker
* Retry logic
* Health checks
* Distributed locking
* Leader election
* Eliminating SPOF
* SLAs / SLOs

